{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 49031,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　消耗は、決して少なくない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The toll is by no means small."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49032,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "マジックが、気遣わしげにため息をついた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Magic sighed with concern."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49033,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そういうわけで、どこかのタイミングで",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That's why, at some point,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49034,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　大きな反攻作戦に出たいの。それが今回……というわけ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "we want to launch a major counteroffensive. That's the plan for this time...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49035,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それはいいが……まさか魔物将軍を全部殺して回れってのか？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That's fine, but... are you saying we have to go around killing all the demon generals?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49036,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　めんどくさいぞ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That's a hassle...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49037,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「奴らにも、指揮官はいるわ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"They have commanders, too."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49038,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それを叩くの」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That's what we need to strike.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49039,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔物大将軍、ツォトン。こいつさえ倒せば、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The Demon Grand General, Tsoton. If we just defeat him,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49040,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ゼスに侵攻してきてる魔軍は崩壊するわ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "the demon army invading Zeth will collapse.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49041,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふん。魔人に比べりゃ雑魚だろ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmph. Compared to the demon lord, he's a pushover."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49042,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ちゃっちゃと殺してやる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I'll kill him quickly.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49043,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それが……居場所が、わからないの」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The thing is... we don't know where he is.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49044,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なんだと？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"What?!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49045,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ランスが来るまでに、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I wanted to somehow find out before Rance arrived,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49046,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんとか掴みたかったんだけど……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "but...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49047,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「やつら、本陣とかないのか？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Do they not have a main camp or something?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49048,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あるけど、そこに籠もってる訳じゃないの。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"They do, but they’re not holed up there."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49049,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　最前線に来たり、後方に行ったり……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They move to the front lines, then back again..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49050,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あちこち、移動してるみたい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It seems they are moving around here and there.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49051,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ちっ、めんどくさいな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Tch, what a hassle."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49052,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　何か手はないのか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Isn't there any way?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49053,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「足取りを追ってもらっては、いるんだけど……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"We're having them tracked, but...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49054,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「よう、新情報入ったぜ…………っと」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hey, I've got new information... hmm.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49055,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「おっ、きくちゃんではないか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh, isn't that Kiku-chan?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49056,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ランスか。来てたのかよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Rance, huh? You came.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49057,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そういえばてるさん、ちぬちゃんとは会ってたのに",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Come to think of it, Teru-san met with Chinu-chan, but"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49058,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　きくちゃんとはろくに顔を合わせてなかったな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "had hardly met with Kiku-chan.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49059,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あー……あたしゃ忍軍率いて別行動だからな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah... I'm leading the ninja army on a separate mission."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49060,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そういう事もあらぁ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That's how it is.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49061,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だがここであったが百年目。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"But meeting here is like a hundred years' reunion."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49062,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　よし、今晩じっくり旧交を温めよう」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Alright, let's rekindle our old friendship tonight.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49063,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「晩ってお前……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Tonight, you say...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49064,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「もちろんセックス！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Of course, sex!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49065,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「バッ……会って三分で",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"B-Before even three minutes after meeting,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49066,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そういう事ほざくんじゃねぇ……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "don't spout things like that...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49067,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……それより、なにか情報があるのでは？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...More importantly, do you have any information?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49068,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「っと、そうだそうだ。魔物大将軍の居場所。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Right, right. The location of the demon grand general."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49069,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　うちの連中が割ってきたぜ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Our guys have broken through.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49070,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「本当！？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Really!?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49071,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああ……ただし、3つな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah... but there are three.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49072,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「3つ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Three?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49073,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「見つけたのはそれらしい魔軍の痕跡、ってだけだ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"What we found are just traces of what seems to be the demon army."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49074,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そのうちのどれかはわかんねぇ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "We don't know which one is his.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49075,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「調べられないの？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Can't you investigate?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49076,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「もちっと時間が要るな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It'll take a bit more time."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49077,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　奴らは数が普通じゃねぇ。もしかしたら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Their numbers aren't normal. Maybe,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49078,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あたしが直接調べなきゃなんねーかも」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I'll have to investigate directly.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49079,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………その間に、またどこかに",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Meanwhile, they might disappear somewhere else again,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49080,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　消えられるかも知れない、んですよね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "right...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49081,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「却下だ却下。待ってられんし",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Rejected, rejected. We can't wait,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49082,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　きくちゃんが無駄な危険を冒すこともない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and Kiku-chan shouldn't take unnecessary risks.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49083,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………ふん」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Hmph.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49084,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「どうしますか、ランス様？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"What will you do, Lord Rance?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49085,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「せっかく来たんだ、俺様が叩き潰してやる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Since I came all this way, I'll crush them myself."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49086,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　成功したら、可愛い魔法使いの女の子を処女で頼む。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "If I succeed, I'll take a cute witch girl, virgin please."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49087,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　4、5人で良いぞ、がはははは」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Four or five will do, gahahaha!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49088,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「バッ……な、何言ってるのよ！　こんな時に……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"B-Ba... what are you saying! At a time like this...!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49089,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　できるわけないでしょ、そんな……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "There's no way we can do that...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49090,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「世界総統の俺様が手ずから戦ってやるのだ。」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I, the Supreme World Leader, will fight personally.\""
    }
  ]
}

